{"tid":1788831,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"14歲中學生墮樓亡","createTime":"2019-12-19T03:57:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-25T01:17:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"fe80857593a17b8cfaaf7fc8baedbcf867a06089","tid":1788831,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:57:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191219/3GVTVDZFB2GDYBPICB7JEGEUOM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191219%2F3GVTVDZFB2GDYBPICB7JEGEUOM%2F&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6k6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=890630ef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191219%2F3GVTVDZFB2GDYBPICB7JEGEUOM%2F&h=632bb860\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191219/3GVTVDZFB2GDYBPICB7JEGEUOM/</a><br />\n<br />\n14歲中學生墮樓亡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191219/large/1576688014_b34b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191219%2Flarge%2F1576688014_b34b.gif&h=33d3fd5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n墮樓男生由救護員送院搶救後證實不治。梁澤岡攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一名身穿校服的14歲中學男生，昨午被發現從紅磡樂民新邨一大廈高處墮落一樓簷篷，當場身受重傷，送往醫院搶救後，證實不治。警方在現場未有撿獲遺書，調查後認為案件無可疑，正追查其墮樓原因。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警未撿獲遺書<br />\n<br />\n現場為紅磡樂民新邨樂善樓，14歲死者在何文田一間中學讀書，事後其家人接獲警方通知趕往醫院，驚聞死訊悲痛不已。<br />\n<br />\n昨日下午1時52分，大廈住客驚聞異響往查看，發現一名穿着校服的學童，重傷昏迷倒卧在大廈一樓簷篷，懷疑他由高處墮下，立即報警。警員及消防救護員接報到場，救援人員爬長梯上簷篷位置，在簷篷替事主包紮急救後，再將他救下由救護車送往伊利沙伯醫院搶救，惜已返魂乏術。<br />\n<br />\n警員在現場沒有撿獲遺書，經上樓調查及聯絡其家人助查後，相信他由大廈一處走廊墮下，事件沒有可疑，正循家庭、學業及感情等多方面追查。一名男親人事後乘警車到醫院認屍，死因有待驗屍後確定。<br />\n<br />\n■記者劉漢權、梁澤岡"},{"pid":"c575bb7de9074c374263221ee2bdfefa9bf482d6","tid":1788831,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:58:19.000Z","msg":"社福罷工<br />\n(今日）19/12  1400-1700<br />\n香港人權法案請願遊行<br />\n<br />\n集合地點更新:<br />\n灣仔港灣道海港中心地下(近灣仔游泳池)<br />\n<br />\n遊行路線<br />\n灣仔至中環九國領事館<br />\n<br />\n澳洲領事館+捷克領事館 / 意大利領事館+荷蘭領事館 / 英國領事館 / 美國領事館+歐盟駐港澳辦事處 / 日本領事館 / 加拿大領事館<br />\n（不反對通知書已獲批）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（今晚）12月19日 1900<br />\n「堅持才看見希望」行動展望集會<br />\n地點： 愛丁堡廣場<br />\n<br />\n(已有不反對通知書)<br />\n社福界罷工委員會"},{"pid":"766aeeb3fb0afbdde9fbcd18f7acb95ba9b10c61","tid":1788831,"uid":244316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T04:02:05.000Z","msg":"rip"},{"pid":"42bcec96545bcbf05c9fb5fa1891ab1ee31b6e88","tid":1788831,"uid":609,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T04:02:56.000Z","msg":"班黑警 乜野都話冇可疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0088c9083da820c6335391bdfabb4ec715dc3abd","tid":1788831,"uid":303677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T04:03:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8825ca36daec6e3d333a2f5c79b23b393312d8e3","tid":1788831,"uid":83907,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T04:04:07.000Z","msg":"一定係黑警逼佢跳<br />\n要求大廈交出cctv紀錄"},{"pid":"ea368dfc6050beb2eb1892e597f9d35cfa5ef9d8","tid":1788831,"uid":245371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T04:05:22.000Z","msg":"唉。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"d746284f35801fd5ce4e00428a4640b404a75bd4","tid":1788831,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T04:06:06.000Z","msg":"哀哉"},{"pid":"5d2e18319af1604890cb3eb0bc0ea31b43abbd76","tid":1788831,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T04:07:30.000Z","msg":"未知原因但無可疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12948651e6af7a5b15fde8645b60d6df54c4dc29","tid":1788831,"uid":235324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d2e18319af1604890cb3eb0bc0ea31b43abbd76","tid":1788831,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T04:07:30.000Z","msg":"未知原因但無可疑<img src=\"/asset